               <code code="34071-1" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="WARNINGS SECTION"/>
               <title>WARNINGS</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>STOP USE IF SKIN BECOMES IRRITATED (PINK, RED DARKER, OR EXCESSIVE PEELING). cONTACT DR. THROWER FOR INSTRUCTIONS. FOR EXTERNAL USE ONLY. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. FEDERAL LAW PROHIBITS THE TRANSFER OF THIS DRUG TO ANY OTHER PERSON OTHER THAN FOR WHOM IT IS PRESCRIBED.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20150522"/>
            </section>
